data.description: Cozy and charming spanish mediterranean single family home in Miami Shores. This lovely three bedroom and two bathroom house has been tastefully updated. Hardwood floors throughout, lots of natural light, wood beam ceilings,tankless water heater, laundry area, large fenced backyard with lots of room for a pool. The property is located in a quiet street with a cul de sac.
